## CALCULATED FIELDS

### Portfolio Metrics
```tableau
// Total Portfolio Balance
SUM([Current Balance])

// Portfolio Growth MoM
(SUM([Current Balance]) - LOOKUP(SUM([Current Balance]), -1)) 
/ LOOKUP(SUM([Current Balance]), -1)

// NPL Ratio
SUM(IF [Is NPL] THEN [Current Balance] END) / SUM([Current Balance])

// PAR 30 Ratio
SUM(IF [Days Past Due] >= 30 THEN [Current Balance] END) / SUM([Current Balance])

// Provision Coverage
SUM([Provision Amount]) / SUM(IF [Is NPL] THEN [Current Balance] END)

// Weighted Average Rate
SUM([Current Balance] * [Interest Rate]) / SUM([Current Balance])

// DPD Bucket
IF [Days Past Due] = 0 THEN 'Current'
ELSEIF [Days Past Due] <= 30 THEN '1-30'
ELSEIF [Days Past Due] <= 60 THEN '31-60'
ELSEIF [Days Past Due] <= 90 THEN '61-90'
ELSE '90+'
END

// Vintage Month (from origination)
DATETRUNC('month', [Origination Date])

// Months on Book
DATEDIFF('month', [Origination Date], [Date])
```

### Financial Metrics
```tableau
// Net Interest Margin
SUM(IF [Account Category] = 'Net Interest Income' THEN [Actual Amount] END)
/ AVG([Earning Assets])

// ROA (Annualized)
(SUM(IF [Account Type] = 'NET_INCOME' THEN [Actual Amount] END) * 12 / [Months YTD])
/ AVG([Total Assets])

// ROE (Annualized)
(SUM(IF [Account Type] = 'NET_INCOME' THEN [Actual Amount] END) * 12 / [Months YTD])
/ AVG([Total Equity])

// Efficiency Ratio
SUM(IF [Account Category] = 'Operating Expenses' THEN [Actual Amount] END)
/ SUM(IF [Account Category] IN ('Net Interest Income', 'Fee Income') THEN [Actual Amount] END)

// Budget Variance %
(SUM([Actual Amount]) - SUM([Budget Amount])) / SUM([Budget Amount])

// YoY Growth
(SUM([Actual Amount]) - SUM([Prior Year Amount])) / SUM([Prior Year Amount])
```

### Deposit Metrics
```tableau
// Cost of Funds
SUM([Accrued Interest]) / SUM([Principal Amount]) * (365 / [Days in Period])

// Loan to Deposit Ratio
SUM([Loan Balance]) / SUM([Deposit Balance])

// Renewal Rate
COUNTD(IF [Is Renewed] THEN [Deposit ID] END) / COUNTD(IF [Is Matured] THEN [Deposit ID] END)

// Days to Maturity Bucket
IF [Days to Maturity] <= 30 THEN '0-30'
ELSEIF [Days to Maturity] <= 60 THEN '31-60'
ELSEIF [Days to Maturity] <= 90 THEN '61-90'
ELSEIF [Days to Maturity] <= 180 THEN '91-180'
ELSEIF [Days to Maturity] <= 360 THEN '181-360'
ELSE '>360'
END
```

